About
-----
This plugin displays English translation if the current UI language translation doesn't exist.

License
-------
This plugin is licensed under the GNU General Public License v2. See the file LICENSE for the complete terms of this license.

System Requirements
-------------------
This plugin is compatible with OJS 2.x version 2.4.7 or newer.

Installation
------------
To install the plugin:
 - copy the plugin tar.gz or zip file to your OJS/plugins/generic directory
 - unzip the plugin inside the plugins/generic directory
 - from your OJS directory execute:
    $ php tools/upgrade.php upgrade
	(NOTE: It is recommended to back up your database first.)
 - enable the plugin by going to:  Home > User > Journal Management > Plugin Management > Generic Plugins and selecting "ENABLE" under "Default Translation"

Contact/Support
---------------
Documentation, bug listings, and updates can be found on this plugin's homepage
at <http://github.com/pkp/defaultTranslation>.

